Do FileOps.$splitpathname(pcPath,lcDrive,lcDirectory,lcFile,lcExtn)
Do ioAttachments.$determineMimeType(lcExtn) Returns lcMimeType
Do ioAttachments.$determineCharSet(lcExtn) Returns lcCharSet
Do ioAttachments.$determineEncoding(lcExtn) Returns lcEncoding
Do ioAttachments.$determineDisposition(lcExtn) Returns lcDisposition

Do ilAttachments.$add(,pcPath,con(lcFile,lcExtn),cAttachAsFile,lcMimeType,lcCharSet,lcEncoding,lcDisposition)

Quit method ilAttachments